@startuml
title ATM management plane (caam)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #DEEEF0
  BorderColor #1F7A8C
}
skinparam ArrowColor #1F7A8C
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #DEEEF0
skinparam noteBorderColor #1F7A8C

[ATM] as ATM
[ATM manager\n(host)] as H

H --> ATM : caam.002 Device Control / caam.014 Configuration Control
ATM --> H : caam.001 Device Report / caam.013 Configuration Report
H --> ATM : caam.003 Key Download Request
ATM --> H : caam.004 Key Download Response
ATM --> H : caam.009 Reconciliation Advice
note bottom of H : caam manages the machine;\ncatp carries its transactions
@enduml
